## Input

```css
// Missing RHS in binary expression should recover
$missing-rhs: 1 + ;

// Dangling unary chain should recover
$dangling-unary: not - ;

// Missing keyword argument value should recover
$kw-args: foo($x: , $y: 1);

// Map pair missing value in parens should recover
$map-missing: (b: , c: 1);

// Map pair trailing colon should recover
$map-trailing: (b: 1, c:);

```


